    <p>For additional strategies, read <a href="https://www.hackingchinese.com/how-to-learn-chinese-characters/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hacking Chinese's character learning guide</a>, and explore <a href="https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/radicals.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YellowBridge's radical reference</a>. For the research behind spaced repetition, see <a href="https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.1815156116" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tabibian et al. (2019) on optimized learning schedules</a> in PNAS. For insights on the <a href="/chinese/blog/simplified-vs-traditional/">simplified vs traditional debate</a>, check our dedicated guide.</p>

